  "texts": [
    "While the absolute judge outperforms the BTL judge, the BTL2 judge bests it in all metrics.",
    "Notably, the Pearson's r and Spearman's ρ double when compared to the base judge.",
    "We observe the same major improvements for BTL and BTL2 judges with Llama base judge.",
    "The results on Nectar dataset are less conclusive.",
    "The BTL2 judge performs comparably to SFT when the base judge is Prometheus, but is outperformed when the base judge is Llama."
